	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So I've been programming my next title, REKT, and I decided to make a little scrolling text screen with a few raster effects on it for the game to show credits, scores, etc. when you stay on the title screen for too long. After finishing it, I feel like it looks pretty cool (especially on a real NES running on a CRT) so I thought I'd share the ROM with you <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br />Let me know what you think of it!

		
